transcription.text:

Speaker 2: Okay. You're in Cicero, New York?

Speaker 1: If you have the pills that you most recently sent, they're going to say 100 on the pill.

Speaker 1: Well, I took one and all it did was give me a headache.

Speaker 1: It is. It doesn't show it as an AGV pill on the Internet.

Speaker 1: The pill... If you have 100 on the pill, that is the right pill. It's not going to say AGV on the pill.

Speaker 2: But like I said, if it's not for you, you can return it. We have a money-back guarantee.

Speaker 1: Okay. Thanks.

Speaker 2: You're welcome. Have a good one.
